<main id="main-content" class="container privacy-page">
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="updated">Last Updated: December 17, 2024</p>

  <section>
    <h2>Introduction</h2>
    <p>MyWebClass.org respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information in compliance with GDPR and other privacy regulations.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Cookies &amp; Tracking</h2>
    <p>We use optional cookies only for anonymous analytics. These cookies help us understand how visitors use the site so we can improve the experience. <strong>Analytics cookies are only activated after user consent.</strong></p>
    
    <h3>Cookie Types:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> Required for site functionality (cookie consent preferences)</li>
      <li><strong>Analytics Cookies:</strong> Optional, anonymous usage tracking (requires consent)</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p>You can manage your cookie preferences using the cookie consent banner that appears on your first visit.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>We use <strong>Plausible Analytics</strong>, a privacy-friendly analytics platform that:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Does <strong>not</strong> use cookies</li>
      <li>Does <strong>not</strong> collect personal data</li>
      <li>Does <strong>not</strong> track you across websites</li>
      <li>Is fully GDPR-compliant</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Analytics tracking is disabled by default and only enabled if you explicitly consent via our cookie banner.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Forms and Submissions</h2>
    <p>When you submit a design demo through our gallery submission form, we collect:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Name:</strong> To identify you as the creator</li>
      <li><strong>Email address:</strong> To contact you about your submission status</li>
      <li><strong>Design style:</strong> The category of your demo</li>
      <li><strong>Demo URL:</strong> Link to your hosted design example</li>
      <li><strong>Screenshot:</strong> Visual preview of your demo</li>
      <li><strong>Description:</strong> Your explanation of design authenticity</li>
    </ul>
    <p>This data is stored securely in our content management system (Sanity CMS) and is used only for educational review and publication purposes. Approved submissions may be displayed publicly in the design gallery.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Data Storage &amp; Security</h2>
    <p>Your submitted content is stored in <strong>Sanity CMS</strong>, a secure cloud-based content platform. We implement industry-standard security measures including:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>HTTPS encryption for all data transmission</li>
      <li>Secure API connections with environment variables</li>
      <li>Access controls for instructor review systems</li>
      <li>Regular security audits and updates</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h3>Data Retention:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Approved submissions:</strong> Retained indefinitely (publicly displayed)</li>
      <li><strong>Rejected submissions:</strong> Deleted after 30 days</li>
      <li><strong>Pending submissions:</strong> Deleted after 90 days if no action taken</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Third-Party Integrations</h2>
    <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
    
    <h3>Sanity CMS</h3>
    <p>For content management and storage of gallery submissions. <a href="https://www.sanity.io/legal/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sanity Privacy Policy</a></p>
    
    <h3>Plausible Analytics</h3>
    <p>For privacy-friendly website analytics (no personal data collected). <a href="https://plausible.io/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Plausible Privacy Policy</a></p>
    
    <h3>Discord</h3>
    <p>For submission notifications to our team (metadata only, no email addresses). <a href="https://discord.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Discord Privacy Policy</a></p>
    
    <h3>CRM Tools</h3>
    <p>For managing participant information and submissions (Airtable/HubSpot). Data is not sold or shared for advertising purposes.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Your Rights (GDPR)</h2>
    <p>Under GDPR, you have the following rights:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Right to Access:</strong> Request a copy of your personal data</li>
      <li><strong>Right to Rectification:</strong> Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
      <li><strong>Right to Erasure:</strong> Request deletion of your data</li>
      <li><strong>Right to Restrict Processing:</strong> Limit how we use your data</li>
      <li><strong>Right to Data Portability:</strong> Receive your data in a portable format</li>
      <li><strong>Right to Object:</strong> Object to processing for marketing/analytics</li>
      <li><strong>Right to Withdraw Consent:</strong> Opt out of analytics at any time</li>
    </ul>
    <p>To exercise any of these rights, please contact us at <strong>privacy@mywebclass.org</strong>. We will respond within 30 days.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>Our website is intended for educational purposes and may be used by students. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13 without parental consent. If you believe we have inadvertently collected such data, please contact us immediately.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. When we make significant changes, we will update the "Last Updated" date and notify users who have submitted to our gallery via email.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>For privacy-related questions or to exercise your GDPR rights, please contact:</p>
    <p>
      <strong>Email:</strong> privacy@mywebclass.org<br>
      <strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://mywebclass.org">https://mywebclass.org</a><br>
      <strong>Response Time:</strong> Within 48 hours for urgent matters, 7 days for general inquiries
    </p>
  </section>

  <div class="privacy-summary">
    <h3>Summary</h3>
    <p><strong>We respect your privacy.</strong> We collect only necessary data for submissions, use privacy-friendly analytics (Plausible), and give you full control over your information. You can manage cookies, request data deletion, or contact us anytime with questions.</p>
  </div>
